{{vgname|刀剑神域 虚空断章|ja=ソードアート・オンライン -ホロウ・フラグメント-|en=Sword Art Online: Hollow Fragment}}是由[[Aquria|Aquria]]開發、[[万代南梦宫娱乐|萬代南夢宮遊戲]]發行的[[角色扮演游戏|角色扮演游戏]]，可在[[PlayStation_Vita|PlayStation Vita]]、[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]、[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]遊玩。本作以[[川原礫|川原礫]][[輕小說|輕小說]]《[[刀劍神域|刀劍神域]]》中的同名[[虚拟现实|虚拟现实]][[大型多人在线角色扮演游戏|大型多人在线角色扮演游戏]]爲場景，世界線獨立於原作，是系列第二部遊戲機遊戲，承《[[刀劍神域_無限瞬間|刀劍神域 無限瞬間]]》之上，啓《[[刀劍神域_Lost_Song|刀劍神域 Lost Song]]》之下。

本作重製版《刀劍神域 Re:虛空斷章》和次作捆綁爲《刀劍神域 导演典藏版》，可在[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]遊玩，2015年7、8月在北美、歐洲、澳洲、中東發行，11月在日本發行。重製版除包含原版游戏所有内容外，还追加了新的剧情、[[頭目_(角色類型)|頭目]]、多人模式，可自定主角性別，提升了人物等级上限<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201508/20150824151432.shtml |title = 《刀剑神域》最新PV Re虚空断章可单独购买 |author = 天楼神威 |date = 2015-08-24 |publisher = 电玩巴士 |language =  |accessdate = 2018-04-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180415190322/http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201508/20150824151432.shtml |archive-date = 2018-04-15 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>。《刀劍神域 Re:虛空斷章》個人電腦版于2018年8月21日在[[Steam|Steam]]推出。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.ali213.net/news/html/2018-2/347771.html |title = 《刀剑神域：虚空断章》PC版发售日公布 预订PC《刀剑神域：夺命凶弹》可免费获赠游戏 |author = cloud |date = 2018-02-23 |publisher = 游侠网 |language =  |accessdate = 2018-04-15 |archive-date = 2020-09-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200926174635/https://www.ali213.net/news/html/2018-2/347771.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>

==概要==
本作延續前作設定，世界線獨立於原作。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/infinity-moment-takes-everything-you-know-about-sword-a-464949599|title=Infinity Moment Takes Everything You Know About Sword Art Online, and Turns It on Its Head|publisher=Kotaku|date=2013-04-02|accessdate=2014-05-02|archive-date=2013-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130729003933/http://kotaku.com/infinity-moment-takes-everything-you-know-about-sword-a-464949599}}</ref>劇情與原作〈艾恩葛朗特〉篇處於相同時間點。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Review: Sword Art Online: Hollow Fragment|url=https://www.destructoid.com/stories/review-sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-279631.phtml|access-date=2020-07-22|website=Destructoid|language=|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414211851/https://www.destructoid.com/stories/review-sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-279631.phtml}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Tech in Asia - Connecting Asia's startup ecosystem|url=https://www.techinasia.com/sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-review-kirito-hero-aincrad|access-date=2020-07-22|website=www.techinasia.com|language=|archive-date=2020-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200723121112/https://www.techinasia.com/sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-review-kirito-hero-aincrad}}</ref>

玩家控制的主角[[桐人|桐人]]被困在死亡遊戲《[[刀劍神域世界觀與設定|刀劍神域]]》中。游戏中人物的死亡也会导致在现实中死去。<ref name="gameinformer" />本作部份內容其實是前作的高清重製<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/PS+Vita/Sword+Art+Online%3A+Hollow+Fragment/news.asp?c=59303|title=Sword Art Online: Hollow Fragment will come bundled with another HD game for SAO fans|publisher=Pocket Gamer|date=2014-05-01|accessdate=2014-05-02|archive-date=2016-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405185935/http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/PS+Vita/Sword+Art+Online%3A+Hollow+Fragment/news.asp?c=59303}}</ref>，包含前作的樓層通關<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2014/05/01/sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-includes-hd-version-sword-art-online-infinity-moment/|title=Sword Art Online: Hollow Fragment Includes An HD Version Of Sword Art Online: Infinity Moment|publisher=Siliconera|date=2014-05-01|accessdate=2014-05-01|archive-date=2014-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502033202/http://www.siliconera.com/2014/05/01/sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-includes-hd-version-sword-art-online-infinity-moment/}}</ref>，以及新的虛空區。<ref name="SAOHF Announced for PS Vita">{{cite web|url=http://gematsu.com/2013/10/sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-announced-for-ps-vita|title=Sword Art Online: Hollow Fragment announced for PS Vita|publisher=Gematsu|date=2013-10-06|accessdate=2014-04-02|archive-date=2014-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140425224228/http://gematsu.com/2013/10/sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-announced-for-ps-vita}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-news/2014/01/09-1/sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-screens-show-battle-system-event-scenes-and-more|title="Sword Art Online: Hollow Fragment" Screens Show Battle System, Event Scenes, and More|publisher=Crunchyroll|date=2014-01-10|accessdate=2020-01-10|archive-date=2020-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200225035915/https://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-news/2014/01/09-1/sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-screens-show-battle-system-event-scenes-and-more}}</ref>

== 玩法 ==
本作有100多个角色供玩家选择，以陪伴玩家完成任务。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2014/02/24/can-befriend-100-characters-sword-art-online-hollow-fragment/|title=You Can Befriend Over 100 Characters In Sword Art Online: Hollow Fragment|publisher=Siliconera|date=2014-02-24|accessdate=2018-04-15|archive-date=2018-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617170026/http://www.siliconera.com/2014/02/24/can-befriend-100-characters-sword-art-online-hollow-fragment/|dead-url=no}}</ref>和前作一样，本作有[[大型多人在线角色扮演游戏|大型多人在线角色扮演游戏]]元素。<ref name="gameinformer">{{cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2014/05/01/duo-of-sword-art-online-games-coming-to-north-america.aspx|title=Duo Of Sword Art Online Games Coming To North America|publisher=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]|date=2014-05-01|accessdate=2017-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170415202732/http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2014/05/01/duo-of-sword-art-online-games-coming-to-north-america.aspx|archive-date=2017-04-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>游戏包含[[戀愛模擬遊戲|恋爱元素]]，并支持最多四人的多人模式。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/133910-Sword-Art-Online-Hollow-Fragment-Arrives-in-North-America-this-Summer|title=Sword Art Online: Hollow Fragment Arrives in North America this Summer|publisher=[[The_Escapist|The Escapist]]|language=|date=2014-04-22|accessdate=2018-04-15|archive-date=2016-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309175550/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/133910-Sword-Art-Online-Hollow-Fragment-Arrives-in-North-America-this-Summer|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

