本作[[Fami通|Fami通]]評分爲32分（滿分40分）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gematsu.com/2014/04/famitsu-review-scores-issue-1324|title=Famitsu Review Scores: Issue 1324|publisher=Gematsu|date=2014-04-15|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140416175910/http://gematsu.com/2014/04/famitsu-review-scores-issue-1324}}</ref>[[PlayStation_Lifestyle|PlayStation Lifestyle]]將日語版評爲9分（滿分10分），認爲該遊戲有足時的內容，沒有明顯影響遊戲體驗的性能問題。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2014/06/30/sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-review-go-virtual-vita-import/|title=Sword Art Online: Hollow Fragment Review – Go Virtual (Vita Import)|publisher=PlayStation Lifestyle|date=2014-06-30|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112031420/https://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2014/06/30/sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-review-go-virtual-vita-import/}}</ref>《[[海峽時報|海峽時報]]》指出本作亞洲版錯誤屢見，如字幕語法、拼寫錯誤，不過還是給了8分（滿分10分）。<ref>{{cite web |last=Tan |first=Colin |url=http://www.straitstimes.com/digital-life/gaming/story/sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-feels-real-mmorpg-20140611 |title=Sword Art Online: Hollow Fragment feels like a real MMORPG |publisher=[[The_Straits_Times|The Straits Times]] |date=2014-06-11 |accessdate=2014-07-05 |archive-date=2014-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140712000550/http://www.straitstimes.com/digital-life/gaming/story/sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-feels-real-mmorpg-20140611 }}</ref>有表明製作團隊已意識到英譯的問題，並表示後作將改進翻譯。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2014/10/29/sword-art-online-lost-song-producer-expect-better-english-translation/|title=Sword Art Online: Lost Song Producer: Expect A Better English Translation|publisher=Siliconera|date=2014-10-29|accessdate=2014-10-29|archive-date=2019-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515124444/https://www.siliconera.com/2014/10/29/sword-art-online-lost-song-producer-expect-better-english-translation/}}</ref>

本作在西方世界發行後，評價好壞參半。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]將PlayStation Vita版評爲67分（滿分100分）。<ref name="MCVITA"/>[[IGN|IGN]]则给出5.5分（滿分10分）的评价，認爲本作戰鬥出彩，但受少年戀愛系統和劣質翻譯拖累。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2014/09/19/sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-review|title=Sword Art Online: Hollow Fragment Review|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2014-09-19|accessdate=2015-10-31|archive-date=2020-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200225035918/https://uk.ign.com/articles/2014/09/19/sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-review}}</ref>[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]給了7分（滿分10分），認爲本作體驗有趣，但可能缺乏重玩的價值。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.destructoid.com/review-sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-279631.phtml|title=Sword Art Online: Hollow Fragment|publisher=Destructoid|date=2014-08-19|accessdate=2014-08-19|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113040454/https://www.destructoid.com/review-sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-279631.phtml}}</ref>而《[[Gaming_Age|Gaming Age]]》則評了B級，稱讚遊戲環境和機制，但指出相機控件有缺陷感。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gaming-age.com/2014/08/sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-review-ps-vita/|title=Sword Art Online: Hollow Fragment review for PS Vita|publisher=Gaming Age|date=2014-08-19|accessdate=2014-08-19|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112030651/https://gaming-age.com/2014/08/sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-review-ps-vita/}}</ref>[[PlayStation_Universe|PlayStation Universe]]打了5.5分（滿分10分），表示本作只能給肯掙扎於無靈感而乏味玩法的鐵桿粉絲提供最佳享受。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.psu.com/review/24494/Sword-Art-Online--Hollow-Fragment-Review/?page=2|title=Sword Art Online: Hollow Fragment Review|publisher=[[PlayStation_Universe|PlayStation Universe]]|date=2014-08-29|accessdate=2015-10-31|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305073836/http://www.psu.com/review/24494/Sword-Art-Online--Hollow-Fragment-Review/?page=2}}</ref>[[GameZone|GameZone]]評分爲8分（滿分10分），稱讚遊戲有很多內容可玩。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamezone.com/reviews/2014/08/19/review-sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-traps-fans-inside-an-mmo-simulator|title=Review: Sword Art Online: Hollow Fragment traps fans inside an MMO simulator|publisher=GameZone|date=2014-08-19|accessdate=2014-08-19|archive-date=2014-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140823173326/http://www.gamezone.com/reviews/2014/08/19/review-sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-traps-fans-inside-an-mmo-simulator}}</ref>[[Twinfinite|Twinfinite]]評分爲4分（滿分5分），批評了陡峭的學習曲線和對話翻譯，同時認爲有積極的戰鬥和遊戲設計。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.twinfinite.net/2014/08/19/sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-review/2/|title=Sword Art Online: Hollow Fragment Review|publisher=Twinfinite|date=2014-08-19|accessdate=2014-08-19|archive-date=2015-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150810013336/http://www.twinfinite.net/2014/08/19/sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-review/2/}}</ref>而[[Attack_of_the_Fanboy|Attack of the Fanboy]]則認爲其只要克服次要缺陷，就有可靠的角色扮演遊戲體驗。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://attackofthefanboy.com/reviews/sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-review/|title=Sword Art Online: Hollow Fragment Review|publisher=Attack of the Fanboy|date=2014-08-19|accessdate=2014-08-19|archive-date=2014-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140820193042/http://attackofthefanboy.com/reviews/sword-art-online-hollow-fragment-review/}}</ref>然而《[[Hardcore_Gamer|Hardcore Gamer]]》將其評爲1.5分（滿分5分），稱其爲「劣質遊戲……日本最墮落的垃圾……草率、破爛、低級軟體」，「故事可怕，戰鬥乏味，翻譯不可原諒」。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2014/08/19/review-sword-art-online-hollow-fragment/99686/|title=Review: Sword Art Online: Hollow Fragment|publisher=Hardcore Gamer|date=2014-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819205635/http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2014/08/19/review-sword-art-online-hollow-fragment/99686/|archive-date=2014-08-19|dead-url=no|access-date=2014-08-19}}</ref>

